# Design System — Pokemon TCG × Exebenus Color Scheme

## Current Problem
The current design uses a **WHITE background** with **RED + BLACK neo-brutal** accents.
It needs to match the Pokemon TCG site: **DARK backgrounds** with **VIBRANT colored elements**.

## Target Color Palette

The `:root` vars at lines 7–77 in `apps/web/src/app/globals.css` need these overrides:

```css
/* BACKGROUND — Dark navy theme */
--bg: #0F0F1A;
--bg-2: #1A1A2E;
--panel: #16213E;
--panel-2: #1E2D4A;
--panel-3: #243450;
--panel-dark: #0B1120;
--navy: #0F172A;
--navy-2: #0B1120;
--navy-3: #1A1A2E;

/* TEXT — Light on dark */
--text: #FFFFFF;
--muted: #8A8FB0;

/* ACCENT — Pokemon Yellow (primary CTA) */
--accent: #FFCB05;
--accent-ink: #0a0a0c;

/* ACCENT 2 — Pokemon Blue (structural) */
--accent-2: #3C5AA6;
--accent-2-ink: #ffffff;

/* RED — Keep for emphasis, danger, type chips */
--red: #E3350D;
--gold: #FFCB05;

/* BORDERS — Subtle light on dark */
--border: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
--border-soft: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);

/* GLOWS — Critical for premium dark aesthetic */
--glow-yellow: 0 0 26px 2px rgba(255,203,5,0.40);
--glow-blue: 0 0 22px 2px rgba(60,90,166,0.35);
--glow-red: 0 0 30px -2px rgba(227,53,13,0.45);
```

## Body Background
```css
html, body {
  background:
    radial-gradient(60px 60px at 12% 22%, rgba(60,90,166,0.15), transparent 70%),
    radial-gradient(closest-side at 92% 8%, rgba(255,203,5,0.08), transparent),
    radial-gradient(closest-side at 4% 90%, rgba(227,53,13,0.12), transparent),
    #0F0F1A;
  color: #FFFFFF;
}
```

## Design Principles
1. **Dark background** (#0F0F1A → #1A1A2E) — everything dark & premium
2. **Pokemon Yellow (#FFCB05) CTAs** — primary buttons glow yellow, NOT red
3. **Pokemon Blue (#3C5AA6)** — nav accents, links, structural elements
4. **Red (#E3350D)** — ONLY for danger/emphasis/type chips
5. **Glassmorphism panels** — semi-transparent dark panels with backdrop-filter: blur
6. **Glow effects** — buttons, cards, borders have colored glow on hover
7. **Nav** — dark with blur, NOT white
8. **High contrast** — vibrant card artwork against dark neutral backgrounds

## Typography
- **Headings**: Space Grotesk (already loaded) — bold, tight tracking
- **Body**: Inter (already loaded) — clean, readable
- **White text** on dark backgrounds
- **Muted light gray** (#8A8FB0) for secondary text
